title: Redmon Double Door Large Freestanding Floor Cabinet, Size 23.5 x 23.5 x 11.75 Inches with Center Adjustable Shelf, Semi Gloss Finish
description: This Double Door Floor Shelf from the Contemporary Country Collection is great for extra storage and organization in any bathroom. This Double Door floor shelf has an adjustable shelf hid behind the door panels. The sleek solid double doors on this floor cabinet are detailed in design and give a little more to the eye appeal. The Contempoary Country Line has many different styles, pieces, and colors to choose from. They are all ready to assemble, with all pieces being easy to assemble in minutes (simple instructions are included). Assembly instructions include 1-minute video links where assistance may be needed. The quality materials used along with a clean contemporary appeal will adorn any décor` for many years. All pieces of the Contemporary Country Collection are sold separately and available in a variety of colors.
